How about a social ride along the mainly traffic free route from Whitstable to  Ramsgate ,taking in the harbour views of Whitstable ,Herne Bay ,Margate and ,Ramsgate .  . Distance about 27 miles .  <br />
<br />
        The subject is thrown open for discussion ,folks .   <br />
